data.description: ***If buyer uses seller's preferred lender, lender will pay for the cost of a 1/0 temporary rate buy-down, meaning the buyer’s 1st 12 monthly payments of the loan will be calculated at a 1% lower rate.*** See full list of updates and features in downloads! Berry Creek Deed Fee is $49 per month (can be applied to Berry Creek County Club Membership). Audio and video recording in the home for the safety of a special needs child. New roof and downspouts 2023...Classic style home with lovely updates and extras in the coveted Reserve section of Berry Creek. Set on a choice, shaded lot with extra space behind, this home has a wall of windows (updated in 2021) to fill the open spaces with natural light that adds flavor to accent wall colors and makes the updated stainless kitchen appliances sparkle.  Don't miss the updated primary bathroom (~$37k spent), the hardwood floors, the theater room, game room, and the newly renovated upstairs flooring.  Everyone will have their own spaces in this home, encouraged by large bedrooms and extra living areas.  For those that work from home, a large study to accommodate everything from executive work to homeschooling. Breaks are wonderful on the shaded back porch, at dawn, or mid-morning as the smell of cappuccino is delivered on the breeze. From textures to trim work, door hardware to ceiling fans...it's ready for you to move in and start your own memories.  An easy golf cart ride to the club, and walking distance to pool and tennis facilities.  Don't miss your chance for a wonderful, affordable option in the Reserve at Berry Creek.
